data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom  2.5 bath home built in 2023 has an open floor plan with a 1st Floor Primary Bedroom with a walk in closet and attached bath . There are hardwood floors throughout with  9' ceilings on the 1st floor. Kitchen includes stainless steel appliances with an island and granite countertops and a tile backsplash. Large covered front porch with a privacy fenced in back yard and off street parking off the alley.
